parameters:
Young girl Amina: No, Lloyd! You absolutely must not train
any further!

Young girl Amina: If you don't keep your promise with Caron-
sama, your body will break down!

Young boy Lloyd: But, for the sake of Father... If I don't
become a respectable noble by the time Mother returns...
Young girl Amina: ...I activate the big sister privilege.

Young girl Amina: I command you to obey your big sister! So,
training is over for today and you will play with me!

Young girl Amina: You must not defy me! Because this is an
order from big sister Amina!

After losing his father, Heis, and mother, Caron, Lloyd
underwent a drastic change. His smile disappeared, and he
engaged in self-destructive training, repeating it over and
over again, and immersing himself in his studies. It was
Amina's role to stop Lloyd, who had become like this.

And so, the big sister privilege was born. It was more of a
plea to Lloyd than a command. Sensing this, Lloyd lowered
his bloodied fist.

Lloyd's abnormal obsession with Caron. He was convinced that
Caron would never return here again. Even though Amina was
young, she understood this.
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置
